@camilonova This project seems to follow [semantic versioning](https://semver.org/). 

An API breaking change requires a Major version release. `watch_login` being removed is a API change which breaks the projects that depend on django-axes. This kind of change shouldn't go into a patch version like 3.0.3. This would be acceptable in 4.0 release, not 3.0.3.

